      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited as a parts car or a major restoration project. The engine is currently non-operational, and the body shows significant signs of age, including heavy rust on the rocker panels and several large dents. The interior has seen better days, with torn upholstery and a cracked dashboard. It will need to be towed from its current location, but it remains a complete vehicle for someone with the right tools and time.",
